# `hilavitkutin-providers`

Default Resource-backed providers for the hilavitkutin scheduler.
Standalone ecosystem crate; consumed by the engine via Kit
installation or direct `builder.resource(...)` wiring, no reverse
dependency. Ships `InternerKit` (an inline-storage `MemoryArena`
wrapped by `StringInterner`). Future modules add ColumnStorage,
Clock, and Memory defaults as consumer demand surfaces.
